OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome occasional brightness
OL,6,Facross Caithness and towards
OL,7,FInverness, but generally a cloudy day
OL,8,Fwith outbreaks of rain, persistent and
OL,9,Fheavy at times across western hills.
OL,10,FThe rain tending to become lighter and
OL,11,Fpatchier later this afternoon.
OL,12,FOccasionally strong southwesterly
OL,13,Fbreeze.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FCloudy with occasional mainly
OL,16,Flight rain at first but becoming dry
OL,17,Fthrough the evening with some clear
OL,18,Fspells developing. Cloud increases
OL,19,Fagain overnight with outbreaks of rain
OL,20,Flater. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,176,160,301,260,100,100
